1
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:11,000
[action music playing]

2
00:00:30,750 --> 00:00:32,708
Hey. What's going on?

3
00:00:33,416 --> 00:00:35,166
Han needs Lotus to help heal.

4
00:00:36,083 --> 00:00:38,250
To repay his mother and father's debts,

5
00:00:38,333 --> 00:00:39,875
the Crown Prince cut him,

6
00:00:39,958 --> 00:00:42,083
and then used the lotus to rebuild him.

7
00:00:42,666 --> 00:00:44,833
- How many pogs were used?
- I don't really know.

8
00:00:44,916 --> 00:00:46,625
The entire place was alight
when I got there.

9
00:00:46,708 --> 00:00:50,416
[old man] It was the Nine Dragons
Divine Fire Barrier. It takes a big toll.

10
00:00:50,500 --> 00:00:51,666
When will he wake?

11
00:00:51,750 --> 00:00:54,500
He's fine. Don't worry, young lady.

12
00:00:54,583 --> 00:00:56,000
[action music continues]

13
00:01:19,416 --> 00:01:23,041
AGENT FROM ABOVE

14
00:01:23,541 --> 00:01:27,708
INTO THE ABYSS

15
00:01:27,791 --> 00:01:28,625
[music fades]

16
00:01:28,708 --> 00:01:30,708
[birds chirping]

17
00:01:35,875 --> 00:01:37,875
[snoring]

18
00:01:45,291 --> 00:01:46,583
Baby, don't go.

19
00:01:50,416 --> 00:01:51,416
[Han Chieh exhales]

20
00:01:58,083 --> 00:01:59,000
[Yeh Tzu] Mr. Han.

21
00:02:00,333 --> 00:02:01,250
You're awake.

22
00:02:02,333 --> 00:02:03,541
How do you feel now?

23
00:02:10,458 --> 00:02:12,458
[pensive music playing]

24
00:02:18,541 --> 00:02:21,375
Are you sure you're well enough
to handle all this?

25
00:02:21,458 --> 00:02:23,583
Whatever it takes, I'm doing it.

26
00:02:23,666 --> 00:02:25,583
So what are you going to do?

27
00:02:26,500 --> 00:02:28,750
DEMON KING OF THE SIXTH HEAVEN ENTICES MAN

28
00:02:28,833 --> 00:02:31,541
Didn't you say Vasavatti has a new agent?

29
00:02:31,625 --> 00:02:34,541
- You don't know anything about this guy.
- I don't care.

30
00:02:34,625 --> 00:02:37,666
If I don't stop that bastard,
more people will get hurt.

31
00:02:38,166 --> 00:02:39,708
CHIEH

32
00:02:39,791 --> 00:02:40,833
Whoa.

33
00:02:41,958 --> 00:02:43,250
Are you happy now?

34
00:02:43,833 --> 00:02:44,791
Hey?

35
00:02:45,625 --> 00:02:46,708
- Hey?
- [bird chirps]

36
00:02:48,791 --> 00:02:50,041
[bird continues chirping]

37
00:02:57,250 --> 00:03:01,125
[Chang Min] "Go to the summit of
Buddha Mountain to strengthen your body."

38
00:03:01,208 --> 00:03:03,333
[dramatic music playing]

39
00:03:03,416 --> 00:03:04,958
[Han Chieh] Buddha Mountain?

40
00:03:07,458 --> 00:03:08,875
Chen Chi-sha.

41
00:03:09,958 --> 00:03:11,500
[Chang Min pants] Fuck.

42
00:03:11,583 --> 00:03:12,666
BUDDHA

43
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:14,916
[Han Chieh] Back then,
after I defeated him,

44
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:17,958
I sealed his magical weapons
in this secure vault.

45
00:03:18,041 --> 00:03:19,791
[dramatic music continues]

46
00:03:28,541 --> 00:03:30,541
[hissing]

47
00:03:35,041 --> 00:03:36,416
Time to retire now.

48
00:03:37,083 --> 00:03:38,708
Stop using this magic.

49
00:03:39,208 --> 00:03:41,625
I'll be the one
to protect you in the future.

50
00:03:43,500 --> 00:03:45,875
[Chi-sha] Do you really think
you're invincible?

51
00:03:50,458 --> 00:03:52,916
[dramatic music continues]

52
00:03:55,958 --> 00:03:57,666
You got lucky this time.

53
00:03:58,166 --> 00:04:01,291
If Vasavatti gets his full demonic power,

54
00:04:01,958 --> 00:04:02,833
you're dead.

55
00:04:08,083 --> 00:04:09,125
[both panting]

56
00:04:10,208 --> 00:04:13,625
[Chang Min] It sounds like
this vault doesn't contain anything good.

57
00:04:13,708 --> 00:04:15,458
Maybe the Crown Prince is playing you?

58
00:04:15,541 --> 00:04:17,541
[Han Chieh] He let
Hsiao-wen bring me a message.

59
00:04:17,625 --> 00:04:20,500
Despite our past,
I don't think he's messing with me.

60
00:04:20,583 --> 00:04:23,083
[Chang Min] I think
you're the one messing with me.

61
00:04:23,166 --> 00:04:24,833
Fuck, I'm exhausted.

62
00:04:24,916 --> 00:04:28,958
[both breathing heavily]

63
00:04:29,041 --> 00:04:30,041
Hey.

64
00:04:31,875 --> 00:04:32,958
Do you have the key?

65
00:04:34,583 --> 00:04:35,625
[bangs lock]

66
00:04:36,791 --> 00:04:38,791
[mysterious music playing]

67
00:04:43,041 --> 00:04:45,041
[music intensifies]

68
00:04:52,708 --> 00:04:53,958
[nervously] Oh shit.

69
00:04:55,541 --> 00:04:57,458
ZERO, ONE, TWO, THREE,
FOUR, FIVE, SIX, SEVEN, EIGHT, NINE

70
00:04:57,541 --> 00:05:00,125
Oh. What the fuck is this?

71
00:05:00,208 --> 00:05:02,208
[mysterious music continues]

72
00:05:15,458 --> 00:05:17,458
[rattling]

73
00:05:20,875 --> 00:05:22,291
[loud thump]

74
00:05:33,833 --> 00:05:35,833
[music crescendos and stops]

75
00:05:37,083 --> 00:05:38,750
[music turns comical]

76
00:05:38,833 --> 00:05:40,375
- [rattling]
- [gasps]

77
00:05:40,458 --> 00:05:42,166
[upbeat music playing]

78
00:05:48,791 --> 00:05:51,125
Whoa, whoa, whoa.

79
00:05:52,291 --> 00:05:53,791
Whoa, whoa, whoa.

80
00:05:54,500 --> 00:05:55,833
What…

81
00:06:00,750 --> 00:06:01,791
Oh my God!

82
00:06:03,833 --> 00:06:04,916
What's this?

83
00:06:05,666 --> 00:06:08,083
[mysterious music playing]

84
00:06:15,416 --> 00:06:16,416
[music fades]

85
00:06:16,500 --> 00:06:18,250
Go, go, go. Come on, come on.

86
00:06:19,125 --> 00:06:20,250
Let's go.

87
00:06:20,333 --> 00:06:23,333
- [keyboard clacking]
- [gunshot over video game]

88
00:06:24,625 --> 00:06:25,458
Incense.

89
00:06:40,083 --> 00:06:42,125
Was it Chi-sha who put you there?

90
00:06:44,625 --> 00:06:45,750
But why?

91
00:06:52,291 --> 00:06:53,125
Me?

92
00:06:54,375 --> 00:06:55,833
A message for me?

93
00:06:57,625 --> 00:06:58,458
Wu…

94
00:06:59,375 --> 00:07:00,541
Wu Tien-chi?

95
00:07:02,583 --> 00:07:03,833
[somber music playing]

96
00:07:03,916 --> 00:07:06,916
Wu Meng-hsueh.

97
00:07:10,291 --> 00:07:11,500
Wu Meng-hsueh?

98
00:07:15,500 --> 00:07:16,750
Check out who this is.

99
00:07:17,916 --> 00:07:20,500
- Yeah, sure. Won't take long.
- Okay.

100
00:07:20,583 --> 00:07:22,583
[somber music continues]

101
00:07:23,291 --> 00:07:25,208
[Hsiao-ming] There on your left. Damn.

102
00:07:27,041 --> 00:07:28,750
Get down, get down, get down.

103
00:07:29,333 --> 00:07:31,166
Don't come in here and mess with me.

104
00:07:31,250 --> 00:07:33,791
Don't do it. Come on, let's go.

105
00:07:34,375 --> 00:07:35,750
- Let's go.
- [Han Chieh] Hsiao-ming.

106
00:07:35,833 --> 00:07:36,791
Huh?

107
00:07:36,875 --> 00:07:38,708
Who pays for the Internet?

108
00:07:39,416 --> 00:07:40,875
[over video game] <i>Watch out. Grenade!</i>

109
00:07:40,958 --> 00:07:42,291
- You, right?
- Mmm.

110
00:07:42,375 --> 00:07:43,708
<i>Fire in the hole!</i>

111
00:07:43,791 --> 00:07:46,916
Then be a big brother,
and look after the little ghost.

112
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,208
- Huh?
- Huh?

113
00:07:48,291 --> 00:07:50,750
- [intriguing music playing]
- Oh. Yeah, sure.

114
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:53,041
- [sighs]
- I'm off.

115
00:07:53,125 --> 00:07:54,208
Bye-bye.

116
00:08:00,125 --> 00:08:01,291
Come on.

117
00:08:06,833 --> 00:08:07,750
You good?

118
00:08:08,250 --> 00:08:10,041
I need to pee.

119
00:08:11,541 --> 00:08:12,416
Huh?

120
00:08:12,500 --> 00:08:14,083
I need to go.

121
00:08:15,125 --> 00:08:17,208
He needs to fucking pee.

122
00:08:17,875 --> 00:08:19,041
- Hey!
- [music stops]

123
00:08:19,541 --> 00:08:21,041
CRIMINAL INFORMATION, NAME: WU MENG-HSUEH

124
00:08:21,125 --> 00:08:24,083
Wu Meng-hsueh changed his name
to Wu Tien-chi.

125
00:08:24,166 --> 00:08:26,375
There's a rumor
he can predict stock market trends.

126
00:08:26,958 --> 00:08:29,541
The market rises and falls
just as he predicts.

127
00:08:29,625 --> 00:08:32,083
He committed murder
when he was a teenager.

128
00:08:33,166 --> 00:08:34,916
[tense music playing]

129
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:38,166
Chen Chi is Vasavatti's new agent.

130
00:08:39,083 --> 00:08:40,791
Chi-sha was just a puppet.

131
00:08:40,875 --> 00:08:42,583
Now that he's dead,

132
00:08:43,291 --> 00:08:45,125
Tien-chi is holding Yu-ching.

133
00:08:47,208 --> 00:08:48,041
But why?

134
00:08:51,625 --> 00:08:53,708
[tense music fades]

135
00:08:55,125 --> 00:08:56,166
[Chao] Mr. Wang.

136
00:09:02,958 --> 00:09:04,416
You'll exhaust yourself.

137
00:09:04,916 --> 00:09:06,375
Go home. Rest.

138
00:09:06,458 --> 00:09:08,250
It's best. You need your strength.

139
00:09:08,833 --> 00:09:09,958
[sighs]

140
00:09:10,041 --> 00:09:11,000
It's fine.

141
00:09:11,750 --> 00:09:13,083
I'll wait here.

142
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,541
The house is empty anyway.

143
00:09:24,250 --> 00:09:26,291
[cell phone vibrating]

144
00:09:32,041 --> 00:09:33,791
- Hello?
- [suspenseful music playing]

145
00:09:33,875 --> 00:09:35,750
[Wu Tien-chi] <i>Are you Yu-ching's dad?</i>

146
00:09:36,458 --> 00:09:38,041
Yes, I am.

147
00:09:38,125 --> 00:09:39,750
<i>I'm her friend from school.</i>

148
00:09:39,833 --> 00:09:43,291
<i>Did you know</i>
<i>Yu-ching's being bullied really badly?</i>

149
00:09:43,375 --> 00:09:45,708
- She's being bullied?
- <i>Mm-hmm.</i>

150
00:09:45,791 --> 00:09:47,875
She's never mentioned this. Why?

151
00:09:48,375 --> 00:09:49,541
Are you her friend?

152
00:09:49,625 --> 00:09:52,500
<i>I know where you can find her,</i>
<i>but I don't want to get into trouble,</i>

153
00:09:52,583 --> 00:09:55,333
<i>so please promise me one thing.</i>

154
00:09:55,416 --> 00:09:57,166
<i>Don't call the cops.</i>

155
00:09:57,250 --> 00:09:59,125
<i>That's the only way I can help you.</i>

156
00:09:59,208 --> 00:10:00,916
Okay. I promise.

157
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:03,000
[suspenseful music continues]

158
00:10:04,541 --> 00:10:05,375
CRIMINAL FILES

159
00:10:05,875 --> 00:10:09,125
Correct, yes.
I handled Meng-hsueh's case back then.

160
00:10:09,208 --> 00:10:10,250
It's been 20 years.

161
00:10:10,333 --> 00:10:12,708
You haven't forgotten the case
in all this time.

162
00:10:13,291 --> 00:10:14,666
I'll never forget.

163
00:10:15,583 --> 00:10:18,416
I could never accept
the verdict of this case.

164
00:10:18,500 --> 00:10:21,708
PRESIDING JUDGE: CHANG HO-CHENG

165
00:10:27,291 --> 00:10:28,791
[suspenseful music continues]

166
00:10:28,875 --> 00:10:29,708
What?

167
00:10:32,125 --> 00:10:33,708
[Chang Min] Please continue.

168
00:10:33,791 --> 00:10:35,875
Wu Meng-hsueh was 15.

169
00:10:36,416 --> 00:10:39,125
The victim was a 16-year-old girl.

170
00:10:40,041 --> 00:10:42,666
She died with her grandma in her own home.

171
00:10:43,500 --> 00:10:44,916
What was the motive?

172
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:46,291
It was sick.

173
00:10:46,875 --> 00:10:49,416
The girl showed signs of sexual assault.

174
00:10:49,500 --> 00:10:53,416
Wu Meng-hsueh claimed they were dating,
yet her grandma forbade it.

175
00:10:53,500 --> 00:10:55,250
His dad was a famous lawyer.

176
00:10:55,750 --> 00:11:00,333
He got a big legal team to exonerate him
using the excuse that he was a minor.

177
00:11:00,958 --> 00:11:03,333
They exploited all sorts
of legal loopholes.

178
00:11:03,833 --> 00:11:06,083
The victim's grandfather
was present in court,

179
00:11:06,166 --> 00:11:09,083
but he couldn't speak
due to a recent stroke.

180
00:11:09,166 --> 00:11:12,208
Wu Meng-hsueh's dad used
various political and business connections

181
00:11:12,291 --> 00:11:14,791
to exert pressure on the judge.

182
00:11:14,875 --> 00:11:17,416
In the end, he received a light sentence.

183
00:11:18,041 --> 00:11:23,166
After the verdict, the grandpa went
into a depression and died soon after.

184
00:11:23,666 --> 00:11:25,750
Wu Meng-hsueh got off lightly.

185
00:11:26,750 --> 00:11:28,625
He was soon released.

186
00:11:28,708 --> 00:11:30,666
[poignant music playing]

187
00:11:30,750 --> 00:11:31,916
[taps table]

188
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:34,958
I'm angry at myself
for not finding justice.

189
00:11:35,708 --> 00:11:37,750
But I'm even angrier at the system.

190
00:11:38,250 --> 00:11:40,708
At what these people can get away with.

191
00:11:47,666 --> 00:11:50,875
PRESIDING JUDGE, CHANG HO-CHENG

192
00:11:57,375 --> 00:12:00,625
[Chang Min] I've arranged to meet
his father's old secretary here.

193
00:12:00,708 --> 00:12:01,708
[music fades]

194
00:12:03,291 --> 00:12:06,750
- [Chang Min sighs]
- You've been acting strange. Why?

195
00:12:10,500 --> 00:12:13,625
The main presiding judge
in Wu Meng-hsueh's case,

196
00:12:14,375 --> 00:12:15,666
it was my father.

197
00:12:16,333 --> 00:12:19,500
- [soft music playing]
- He didn't often talk about his work.

198
00:12:20,541 --> 00:12:23,375
He suffered from depression
when I was in high school,

199
00:12:23,458 --> 00:12:25,458
and he died not long after that.

200
00:12:25,958 --> 00:12:29,333
I remember him saying,
"I'm sorry, I'm sorry."

201
00:12:29,916 --> 00:12:31,375
Now I know the reason.

202
00:12:32,708 --> 00:12:37,000
He was obviously consumed with guilt
all the way to his deathbed.

203
00:12:38,458 --> 00:12:39,958
He made a mistake.

204
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,416
He's only human.

205
00:12:42,916 --> 00:12:44,916
[music turns sad]

206
00:12:45,458 --> 00:12:48,416
I want to send this scumbag to jail.

207
00:12:50,000 --> 00:12:51,083
To jail.

208
00:12:51,583 --> 00:12:54,875
People like that
should go directly to hell.

209
00:12:57,041 --> 00:12:58,208
Worse than hell.

210
00:13:01,416 --> 00:13:03,375
[music fades]

211
00:13:03,458 --> 00:13:06,458
Ms. Liu, I'm the officer
who talked to you on the phone.

212
00:13:06,541 --> 00:13:07,875
This is my associate.

213
00:13:08,750 --> 00:13:12,000
I'd like to talk to you
about your employer, Mr. Wu's son.

214
00:13:12,083 --> 00:13:13,416
Wu Meng-hsueh.

215
00:13:13,500 --> 00:13:16,208
[eerie music playing]

216
00:13:23,708 --> 00:13:24,541
Ms Liu.

217
00:13:29,291 --> 00:13:31,291
[Ms. Liu breathes nervously]

218
00:13:32,375 --> 00:13:33,916
What do you want to know?

219
00:13:34,500 --> 00:13:36,833
Wu Meng-hsueh changed his identity.

220
00:13:36,916 --> 00:13:38,916
What else can you tell us about him?

221
00:13:39,416 --> 00:13:43,041
They were an influential
and powerful family.

222
00:13:43,125 --> 00:13:45,250
Why did he learn Wumeng magic?

223
00:13:46,250 --> 00:13:47,541
Because…

224
00:13:49,208 --> 00:13:51,000
that girl's grandfather

225
00:13:51,750 --> 00:13:53,250
haunted him in jail.

226
00:13:53,958 --> 00:13:55,000
Go away.

227
00:13:55,083 --> 00:13:56,166
Get lost.

228
00:13:57,750 --> 00:14:00,583
You killed my granddaughter and wife.

229
00:14:00,666 --> 00:14:03,000
I'm going to haunt you
till the day you die.

230
00:14:03,083 --> 00:14:06,083
Here or in the Underworld,
I'll make you pay.

231
00:14:06,166 --> 00:14:08,541
- [sobbing]
- [eerie music continues]

232
00:14:08,625 --> 00:14:12,166
I will personally ensure
you suffer in hell!

233
00:14:12,875 --> 00:14:15,375
Wu Meng-hsueh sought help from his dad.

234
00:14:15,458 --> 00:14:17,166
So Mr. Wu found an expert,

235
00:14:17,250 --> 00:14:21,166
and trapped the soul of the girl's
grandfather in a sandalwood burner,

236
00:14:21,250 --> 00:14:23,583
and sealed it inside with a talisman.

237
00:14:25,208 --> 00:14:27,666
[Han Chieh] Do you know
where this incense burner is now?

238
00:14:29,458 --> 00:14:33,166
I don't. I only know that after
Wu Meng-hsueh was released from prison,

239
00:14:33,250 --> 00:14:35,208
he traveled all over the world.

240
00:14:36,541 --> 00:14:38,083
He had one goal to achieve.

241
00:14:38,833 --> 00:14:42,833
To be completely free from punishment
both in the Human Realm and in hell.

242
00:14:43,666 --> 00:14:46,708
He started learning all sorts
of techniques and witchcraft,

243
00:14:46,791 --> 00:14:49,208
including the most evil Wumeng Technique.

244
00:14:49,291 --> 00:14:51,000
[eerie music continues]

245
00:14:52,500 --> 00:14:54,166
[Tien-chi's father] <i>What have you done?</i>

246
00:14:54,250 --> 00:14:59,500
We had four competitors, and now all four
of them mysteriously die at the same time.

247
00:14:59,583 --> 00:15:02,750
This is a great situation for us.
What are you upset about?

248
00:15:02,833 --> 00:15:08,041
Meng-hsueh, stop engaging
in these shady practices.

249
00:15:08,125 --> 00:15:10,208
- [sighs]
- If you don't stop…

250
00:15:10,291 --> 00:15:11,291
[music stops]

251
00:15:12,958 --> 00:15:14,750
I'll change my will.

252
00:15:14,833 --> 00:15:17,791
And when the time comes,
you won't see a penny.

253
00:15:21,125 --> 00:15:22,458
Why don't you try it?

254
00:15:22,958 --> 00:15:25,083
[dramatic music playing]

255
00:15:25,166 --> 00:15:27,041
You might find you…

256
00:15:27,541 --> 00:15:29,166
have a little accident,

257
00:15:29,916 --> 00:15:31,250
if you change that will.

258
00:15:31,875 --> 00:15:32,750
Uh…

259
00:15:33,375 --> 00:15:35,875
[father] I should've
let the judge find you guilty.

260
00:15:40,125 --> 00:15:42,125
[dramatic music continues]

261
00:15:42,833 --> 00:15:44,500
[breathes nervously]

262
00:15:45,958 --> 00:15:48,041
After that, Mr. Wu closed the firm.

263
00:15:50,041 --> 00:15:52,333
Soon after that, I retired.

264
00:15:52,833 --> 00:15:55,291
I haven't heard anything about them since.

265
00:16:03,333 --> 00:16:04,333
[Han Chieh] Oh.

266
00:16:05,458 --> 00:16:06,958
We must find it.

267
00:16:08,083 --> 00:16:09,166
Why?

268
00:16:10,416 --> 00:16:14,791
The one thing he's scared of
is karma. It could destroy him.

269
00:16:15,833 --> 00:16:19,250
You mean if
the girl's grandpa reports him,

270
00:16:19,750 --> 00:16:23,083
when Tien-chi dies
he'll be accountable for his crimes.

271
00:16:23,583 --> 00:16:26,333
Mmm. Can you find where it's hidden?

272
00:16:27,500 --> 00:16:29,791
- [music fades]
- I'm digging up all we can now.

273
00:16:29,875 --> 00:16:31,375
He's got a passport,

274
00:16:31,458 --> 00:16:35,958
and foreign companies are
in control of all of his assets.

275
00:16:36,041 --> 00:16:37,500
Our Vasavatti.

276
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:40,500
He's cunning and smart.

277
00:16:41,083 --> 00:16:43,833
Smart. So what? He's an evil creature.

278
00:16:43,916 --> 00:16:46,291
You're not so smart, but better than him.

279
00:16:46,375 --> 00:16:47,875
You're the brainless one here.

280
00:16:47,958 --> 00:16:49,875
- [phone vibrating]
- Ouch, that hurts.

281
00:16:51,500 --> 00:16:53,208
INVESTIGATION TEAM ONE

282
00:16:53,291 --> 00:16:54,375
[tense music playing]

283
00:16:54,458 --> 00:16:55,666
- Calm down.
- You bastard!

284
00:16:55,750 --> 00:16:58,833
- Where's my daughter? Where is she?
- Sir, calm down.

285
00:16:58,916 --> 00:17:00,916
[struggling]

286
00:17:03,375 --> 00:17:04,208
Good job.

287
00:17:06,791 --> 00:17:09,458
The man he assaulted,
he has a drug conviction.

288
00:17:09,541 --> 00:17:12,916
Mr. Wang got a call saying
his daughter was being bullied,

289
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:16,166
saying it's the reason
for his daughter's kidnapping.

290
00:17:16,250 --> 00:17:19,500
- He told him her location?
- It was owned by Tien-chi.

291
00:17:19,583 --> 00:17:23,083
It's where he killed that girl,
and where he killed the girl's grandma.

292
00:17:23,166 --> 00:17:25,750
That's where he found this boy,
and assaulted him.

293
00:17:25,833 --> 00:17:27,750
[tense music intensifies]

294
00:17:27,833 --> 00:17:30,333
Always using others to do things.

295
00:17:31,208 --> 00:17:32,250
His typical MO.

296
00:17:33,375 --> 00:17:36,958
Chao's invited him to come
and have a chat with us.

297
00:17:37,041 --> 00:17:38,041
[sigh]

298
00:17:38,125 --> 00:17:40,750
I bought this property a long time ago.

299
00:17:40,833 --> 00:17:43,000
It's been empty now for years.

300
00:17:43,083 --> 00:17:46,000
[scoffs] I had no idea
someone would cause trouble there.

301
00:17:46,583 --> 00:17:48,208
Why did you buy that property?

302
00:17:48,291 --> 00:17:50,000
[music turns eerie]

303
00:17:52,458 --> 00:17:53,625
[chuckles]

304
00:17:53,708 --> 00:17:55,791
The location's very good,

305
00:17:55,875 --> 00:17:59,583
and I thought that an investment
in that area would be a good idea.

306
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:03,166
[curious music playing]

307
00:18:04,333 --> 00:18:07,291
So, can I help
with anything else, officers?

308
00:18:10,250 --> 00:18:11,458
[chuckles softly]

309
00:18:11,541 --> 00:18:13,625
[music fades]

310
00:18:13,708 --> 00:18:15,375
- Thank you.
- Bye.

311
00:18:18,500 --> 00:18:20,333
You're letting him go?

312
00:18:20,416 --> 00:18:22,041
We can't detain him.

313
00:18:22,125 --> 00:18:25,250
We have no direct evidence
to prove his involvement.

314
00:18:26,250 --> 00:18:28,666
And we've traced the number
that called Mr. Wang.

315
00:18:28,750 --> 00:18:30,375
It was from outside the country.

316
00:18:30,875 --> 00:18:33,333
So, we can't be sure
that it was him who called.

317
00:18:34,166 --> 00:18:36,375
- [sighs] Did--
- All right.

318
00:18:36,458 --> 00:18:38,666
Follow him, 24-7.

319
00:18:39,166 --> 00:18:40,125
Will do.

320
00:18:44,791 --> 00:18:46,791
[dramatic music playing]

321
00:18:48,958 --> 00:18:49,958
Hello.

322
00:18:51,458 --> 00:18:52,583
Don't play dumb with me.

323
00:18:54,625 --> 00:18:55,583
Oh.

324
00:18:56,083 --> 00:18:58,166
[chuckling]

325
00:18:59,916 --> 00:19:00,916
[sighs]

326
00:19:02,833 --> 00:19:04,541
Mmm.

327
00:19:06,291 --> 00:19:07,708
You're pretty special.

328
00:19:08,208 --> 00:19:11,625
You faced Chen Chi-sha,
and lived to tell the tale.

329
00:19:12,458 --> 00:19:13,458
Mmm.

330
00:19:14,125 --> 00:19:17,666
Tell Vasavatti I'm wise to his tricks,

331
00:19:17,750 --> 00:19:19,916
and I'm ready to engage.

332
00:19:20,416 --> 00:19:21,666
But release Yu-ching.

333
00:19:22,250 --> 00:19:25,375
And observe some rules,
like not harming innocents.

334
00:19:25,458 --> 00:19:26,791
[dramatic music continues]

335
00:19:26,875 --> 00:19:30,291
Which I know you so enjoy doing,
so let's have it out.

336
00:19:30,375 --> 00:19:34,000
You win, you can have my life.

337
00:19:36,791 --> 00:19:39,291
[music builds]

338
00:19:39,375 --> 00:19:41,416
[inhales]

339
00:19:41,500 --> 00:19:43,333
Oh, sounds quite appealing.

340
00:19:44,583 --> 00:19:46,041
But you don't know me very well.

341
00:19:46,958 --> 00:19:47,916
Let me tell you.

342
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:52,208
What I hate most in life
is having to follow rules.

343
00:19:53,791 --> 00:19:55,375
Take those guys over there.

344
00:19:56,250 --> 00:19:59,750
They have to follow the rules
every time they do something,

345
00:20:00,916 --> 00:20:03,625
as they live their boring lives.

346
00:20:03,708 --> 00:20:05,083
They long for what?

347
00:20:05,708 --> 00:20:07,708
- Freedom.
- [dramatic music playing]

348
00:20:07,791 --> 00:20:09,958
Freedom is everything.

349
00:20:11,250 --> 00:20:12,250
Right?

350
00:20:13,958 --> 00:20:14,958
[chuckles]

351
00:20:15,541 --> 00:20:17,416
Oh, I heard your pogs are amazing.

352
00:20:20,625 --> 00:20:22,166
I can't wait.

353
00:20:28,541 --> 00:20:30,041
[techno music playing]

354
00:20:30,125 --> 00:20:32,166
[vehicle revving]

355
00:20:42,916 --> 00:20:45,333
[man] Hello, sir. This way, please.

356
00:20:46,958 --> 00:20:48,750
The VIP has arrived.

357
00:20:48,833 --> 00:20:50,791
[techno music continues]

358
00:21:14,333 --> 00:21:15,666
[music ends]

359
00:21:15,750 --> 00:21:18,666
[Yeh Tzu] The weather's turned cold.
Rug up tight at night.

360
00:21:18,750 --> 00:21:20,208
[laughs] Thank you.

361
00:21:20,291 --> 00:21:23,166
You forgot one thing.
Wear socks when you sleep!

362
00:21:23,666 --> 00:21:25,125
- Bye-bye.
- [laughs] Bye.

363
00:21:25,208 --> 00:21:27,208
[eerie music playing]

364
00:21:30,208 --> 00:21:31,208
[sighs]

365
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:38,333
[wind blows]

366
00:21:38,416 --> 00:21:40,500
[indistinct female cry]

367
00:21:49,833 --> 00:21:51,250
[old man vocalizing]

368
00:21:53,958 --> 00:21:55,458
Back already?

369
00:21:59,500 --> 00:22:01,541
Hey, Yeh Tzu.

370
00:22:02,625 --> 00:22:03,958
Yeh Tzu. Wait.

371
00:22:05,458 --> 00:22:06,500
Yeh Tzu.

372
00:22:06,583 --> 00:22:08,625
- [screams]
- [music intensifies]

373
00:22:16,375 --> 00:22:18,375
[action music playing]

374
00:22:21,166 --> 00:22:22,958
[red ghost] Jump off.

375
00:22:23,041 --> 00:22:24,333
Jump off.

376
00:22:25,083 --> 00:22:26,000
Jump!

377
00:22:26,625 --> 00:22:27,625
Jump now.

378
00:22:27,708 --> 00:22:28,708
Now, do it!

379
00:22:28,791 --> 00:22:31,125
You bastard! What do you want?

380
00:22:32,750 --> 00:22:34,458
[music recedes]

381
00:22:36,458 --> 00:22:37,291
[giggles]

382
00:22:38,125 --> 00:22:40,291
- [action music continues]
- Hey, hey, hey!

383
00:22:41,583 --> 00:22:43,583
[music crescendos and stops]

384
00:22:47,916 --> 00:22:48,875
[Han Chieh groans]

385
00:22:52,375 --> 00:22:53,458
[old man] Yeh Tzu.

386
00:22:54,041 --> 00:22:55,166
Yeh Tzu.

387
00:22:59,375 --> 00:23:00,375
Look there.

388
00:23:02,416 --> 00:23:05,000
[slow action music playing]

389
00:23:07,083 --> 00:23:09,916
[chuckling]

390
00:23:18,416 --> 00:23:21,250
[Wu Tien-chi chuckling]

391
00:23:23,625 --> 00:23:25,625
[yawns]

392
00:23:25,708 --> 00:23:27,708
[music fades]

393
00:23:41,083 --> 00:23:43,083
[techno music playing]

394
00:23:54,958 --> 00:23:56,500
[Wu Tien-chi and woman groan]

395
00:23:56,583 --> 00:23:57,750
What do you want?

396
00:23:57,833 --> 00:23:59,000
[tutting]

397
00:24:00,541 --> 00:24:01,750
[laughs]

398
00:24:02,250 --> 00:24:04,166
How do you like my new security?

399
00:24:04,250 --> 00:24:06,000
She's pretty cute, isn't she?

400
00:24:06,625 --> 00:24:09,000
I've always felt bad for Chen Chi-sha.

401
00:24:09,083 --> 00:24:12,750
I want to give him a goddaughter.
Do you think he'd like Yeh Tzu?

402
00:24:12,833 --> 00:24:14,041
You bastard!

403
00:24:14,125 --> 00:24:16,500
- Just try it, and I'll kill you now.
- [laughing]

404
00:24:17,833 --> 00:24:19,625
[techno music continues]

405
00:24:20,875 --> 00:24:22,791
You've never killed a human?

406
00:24:23,583 --> 00:24:29,416
[laughs] You've killed so many demons,
but you've never killed a human?

407
00:24:30,000 --> 00:24:32,083
- Do you wanna try it?
- [tense music plays]

408
00:24:32,666 --> 00:24:35,041
All you have to do is throw me down there.

409
00:24:35,125 --> 00:24:37,208
You see, you're just like me.

410
00:24:38,041 --> 00:24:41,416
- You're the same as me. No different.
- [Chang Min] Han.

411
00:24:41,500 --> 00:24:42,875
- Han, cool it, man.
- Right?

412
00:24:42,958 --> 00:24:44,250
- [Chang Min] Come on.
- Huh?

413
00:24:44,750 --> 00:24:49,083
Huh? You love to make trouble, don't you?
But I think you're just all talk.

414
00:24:49,166 --> 00:24:52,583
If it wasn't Chi-sha pulling your chain,
you'd be nothing.

415
00:24:52,666 --> 00:24:54,666
[tense music continues]

416
00:24:57,958 --> 00:25:00,791
Officer, with all due respect,

417
00:25:00,875 --> 00:25:05,000
your corrupt, incompetent unit
can't touch me.

418
00:25:05,500 --> 00:25:07,250
See you in the afterlife.

419
00:25:07,333 --> 00:25:10,416
Is that it? Is that all you've got to say?

420
00:25:10,500 --> 00:25:13,125
I can't imagine why someone
like Vasavatti would get

421
00:25:13,208 --> 00:25:15,458
someone like you to be his successor.

422
00:25:15,541 --> 00:25:17,875
You're quite pathetic. Hmm?

423
00:25:22,458 --> 00:25:25,125
Chen Chi-sha was a useless old man.

424
00:25:25,208 --> 00:25:27,791
I'm the one who made him kill people.

425
00:25:28,375 --> 00:25:30,541
We're not on the same level, okay?

426
00:25:30,625 --> 00:25:31,916
You can't touch me.

427
00:25:32,000 --> 00:25:34,833
Not with the law or your magic.

428
00:25:34,916 --> 00:25:35,875
You want blood?

429
00:25:35,958 --> 00:25:37,958
Maybe I should kill Yeh Tzu next.

430
00:25:38,541 --> 00:25:40,833
- You--
- Han, let's go. Han, forget it.

431
00:25:40,916 --> 00:25:42,875
- [laughing]
- Come on.

432
00:25:42,958 --> 00:25:45,791
- Han. Come on, out.
- [Wu Tien-chi] Oh, come on, don't go!

433
00:25:45,875 --> 00:25:48,541
- [tense music intensifies]
- [laughing menacingly]

434
00:25:53,458 --> 00:25:55,750
[Chang Min] Come on,
don't let him get to you. It's okay.

435
00:25:55,833 --> 00:25:57,833
Here, let me get the door. Get in.

436
00:25:57,916 --> 00:26:00,291
Get in there. Mind your head.

437
00:26:00,375 --> 00:26:02,333
Yeah. Now sit, relax.

438
00:26:03,083 --> 00:26:04,625
- [sighs]
- [door closes]

439
00:26:05,291 --> 00:26:07,791
Low blood sugar,
I think makes you irritable.

440
00:26:08,666 --> 00:26:09,708
Hmm?

441
00:26:27,333 --> 00:26:28,208
Chao.

442
00:26:28,791 --> 00:26:30,000
Wait for it.

443
00:26:30,083 --> 00:26:34,041
Thanks to Mr. Han here,
we've got grounds for a search warrant.

444
00:26:34,541 --> 00:26:36,000
Mm-hmm.

445
00:26:36,500 --> 00:26:38,041
I'll send it to you later.

446
00:26:41,458 --> 00:26:43,166
[chuckles]

447
00:26:44,208 --> 00:26:45,458
What's funny?

448
00:26:50,541 --> 00:26:53,208
[Wu Tien-chi] <i>Chen Chi-sha was</i>
<i>a useless old man.</i>

449
00:26:53,291 --> 00:26:56,500
<i>- I'm the one who made him kill people.</i>
- [funky music plays]

450
00:27:04,500 --> 00:27:08,416
[Chao] <i>Mr. Chen agreed to an emergency</i>
<i>search of Wu Tien-chi's home tomorrow.</i>

451
00:27:08,500 --> 00:27:09,958
<i>Aside from the recording,</i>

452
00:27:10,041 --> 00:27:14,291
<i>several people at the nightclub</i>
<i>also saw him conversing with Chen Chi-sha.</i>

453
00:27:25,750 --> 00:27:26,666
[Chao grunts]

454
00:27:28,208 --> 00:27:31,666
I found several of these talismans hidden
all over the house.

455
00:27:32,166 --> 00:27:33,958
Is this what you were looking for?

456
00:27:38,125 --> 00:27:39,583
[soft music playing]

457
00:27:39,666 --> 00:27:40,791
[Han Chieh] Mmm.

458
00:27:40,875 --> 00:27:41,750
Be careful.

459
00:27:41,833 --> 00:27:43,125
This is evidence.

460
00:27:43,750 --> 00:27:45,833
After you're done, it needs to be filed.

461
00:27:54,583 --> 00:27:56,750
[yawning] So what are you planning to do?

462
00:27:58,750 --> 00:28:02,708
I'll release him
once I secure a Command Token.

463
00:28:02,791 --> 00:28:04,833
- [tense music playing]
- Mm-hmm.

464
00:28:06,541 --> 00:28:08,916
We finally got something on him.

465
00:28:09,000 --> 00:28:10,791
Tien-chi is toast.

466
00:28:19,291 --> 00:28:21,166
TAIPEI CITY STREET MAP

467
00:28:21,250 --> 00:28:23,250
[low tense music continues]

468
00:28:24,125 --> 00:28:25,750
[Chang Min] Hey, I don't get it.

469
00:28:25,833 --> 00:28:28,958
Tien-chi lied to the girl's father
about the real kidnapper.

470
00:28:29,041 --> 00:28:31,583
He chose his own apartment
as the location,

471
00:28:31,666 --> 00:28:33,458
where he had killed before.

472
00:28:33,541 --> 00:28:34,750
What's his game?

473
00:28:35,791 --> 00:28:37,333
<i>The same location</i>

474
00:28:38,250 --> 00:28:40,500
<i>where he committed murder before.</i>

475
00:28:41,916 --> 00:28:44,041
<i>Why? What's he up to?</i>

476
00:28:44,125 --> 00:28:45,791
[Chi-sha] <i>That girl, she's not here.</i>

477
00:28:45,875 --> 00:28:48,666
There are many uses for Yu-ching.

478
00:28:50,583 --> 00:28:53,791
[Han Chieh] <i>Tien-chi's apartment,</i>
<i>Heilung Hall,</i>

479
00:28:53,875 --> 00:28:56,583
<i>and where A-Fu said</i>
<i>he stole the vital spirits.</i>

480
00:28:56,666 --> 00:28:58,291
PAOAN TEMPLE, LANTE TEMPLE, FUHE TEMPLE

481
00:28:58,375 --> 00:29:01,333
<i>At each different location,</i>
<i>there were strange deaths.</i>

482
00:29:02,041 --> 00:29:03,125
[music builds]

483
00:29:07,583 --> 00:29:08,833
Give me a pen. A pen.

484
00:29:13,458 --> 00:29:15,416
[action music playing]

485
00:29:15,916 --> 00:29:17,375
HEILUNG HALL

486
00:29:22,875 --> 00:29:23,708
FUHE TEMPLE

487
00:29:23,791 --> 00:29:24,958
LANCHEN TEMPLE

488
00:29:25,750 --> 00:29:26,583
PAOAN TEMPLE

489
00:29:30,583 --> 00:29:32,083
[Chang Min] This is…

490
00:29:32,166 --> 00:29:33,291
A formation.

491
00:29:33,375 --> 00:29:34,916
[thunder cracking]

492
00:29:43,416 --> 00:29:44,791
Fuck.

493
00:29:46,041 --> 00:29:47,833
How did I miss that?

494
00:29:47,916 --> 00:29:51,708
He was setting up the formation
to break the restriction of the seal,

495
00:29:51,791 --> 00:29:54,916
so he can channel Vasavatti's spirit
into the Human Realm.

496
00:29:58,083 --> 00:29:59,041
[bird chirps]

497
00:29:59,125 --> 00:30:01,625
[music fades]

498
00:30:02,458 --> 00:30:05,166
[Chang Min] "The corpse demons are
about to be formed."

499
00:30:05,250 --> 00:30:07,416
- "The full moon is approaching."
- [Han Chieh] Full moon.

500
00:30:07,500 --> 00:30:09,583
[dramatic music playing]

501
00:30:09,666 --> 00:30:11,583
Vasavatti appeared at full moon.

502
00:30:13,416 --> 00:30:14,708
[cries]

503
00:30:14,791 --> 00:30:16,458
[action music playing]

504
00:30:17,250 --> 00:30:22,083
You got lucky this time. If Vasavatti gets
his full demonic power, you're dead.

505
00:30:23,166 --> 00:30:25,791
Full moon, magical formation, center.

506
00:30:26,916 --> 00:30:27,916
I get it.

507
00:30:28,500 --> 00:30:30,583
Five years ago, I defeated him,

508
00:30:30,666 --> 00:30:34,041
<i>only because I interrupted</i>
<i>the Demon King's world invasion.</i>

509
00:30:34,583 --> 00:30:38,791
<i>This completed formation will enable</i>
<i>Vasavatti to obtain his full power,</i>

510
00:30:39,500 --> 00:30:43,041
<i>using the portal</i>
<i>when the moon is at its most yin.</i>

511
00:30:44,125 --> 00:30:48,041
[demonically] If you delay me,
I'll bring you to hell.

512
00:30:48,666 --> 00:30:49,875
He's gonna try it again.

513
00:30:52,083 --> 00:30:53,083
WANG YU-CHING, HEILUNG HALL

514
00:30:53,166 --> 00:30:55,041
The portal, where is it?

515
00:30:55,125 --> 00:30:57,125
[dramatic music playing]

516
00:30:57,875 --> 00:31:00,291
[Han Chieh] In the center
of the formation,

517
00:31:01,041 --> 00:31:02,625
<i>Dongfeng Market.</i>

518
00:31:05,958 --> 00:31:10,250
Right from the start, his target was
always you and the Dongfeng Market.

519
00:31:10,333 --> 00:31:12,083
[music continues]

520
00:31:17,208 --> 00:31:20,166
This formation, it's not complete yet.

521
00:31:20,250 --> 00:31:23,791
The offering in the final location
will be Yu-ching.

522
00:31:23,875 --> 00:31:25,625
GOLDEN LAKE PLAZA

523
00:31:26,208 --> 00:31:27,833
We'll stake out the market.

524
00:31:28,541 --> 00:31:30,833
There are thousands
of households where he can hide.

525
00:31:30,916 --> 00:31:32,583
An impossible task.

526
00:31:38,750 --> 00:31:40,500
It's a terrifying way to die.

527
00:31:41,208 --> 00:31:42,583
We must stop this.

528
00:31:43,166 --> 00:31:47,583
The source of the formation's dark power
is the terror these victims felt.

529
00:31:49,958 --> 00:31:54,875
He's keeping Yu-ching alive
until a specific time and location.

530
00:31:54,958 --> 00:31:56,958
A few days before the full moon,

531
00:31:57,041 --> 00:31:58,375
There's still time.

532
00:31:58,458 --> 00:32:00,458
[dramatic music continues]

533
00:32:01,625 --> 00:32:05,500
GOLDEN LAKE PLAZA

534
00:32:05,583 --> 00:32:07,583
[music fades]

535
00:32:07,666 --> 00:32:09,666
[metal clicking]

536
00:32:15,083 --> 00:32:17,000
[whistling and flicking lighter]

537
00:32:32,666 --> 00:32:34,666
[music turns eerie]

538
00:32:36,416 --> 00:32:38,250
[growling]

539
00:33:05,500 --> 00:33:07,500
[music fades]

540
00:33:09,083 --> 00:33:11,083
[continues growling]

541
00:33:15,375 --> 00:33:18,000
- Does our agreement still stand?
- You're useless.

542
00:33:18,083 --> 00:33:21,708
You're scared of that old man
filing a complaint against you.

543
00:33:22,750 --> 00:33:25,291
Provided you handle the matter well,

544
00:33:25,375 --> 00:33:29,125
it matters little what you did
in the Human Realm,

545
00:33:29,208 --> 00:33:32,041
- You will not be punished.
- [dramatic music playing]

546
00:33:32,125 --> 00:33:35,500
Even if you go to hell after you die,

547
00:33:36,875 --> 00:33:42,166
you must be well-prepared
to bring me the thing that I want.

548
00:33:42,250 --> 00:33:44,208
[Tien-chi] <i>I've made all the arrangements.</i>

549
00:33:46,041 --> 00:33:47,541
<i>I tested it today.</i>

550
00:33:49,250 --> 00:33:52,416
Han, Yeh Tzu is being possessed.

551
00:33:53,458 --> 00:33:54,583
What do you want?

552
00:33:54,666 --> 00:33:57,333
[Tien-chi] <i>That brat cares</i>
<i>a lot about Yeh Tzu.</i>

553
00:33:58,041 --> 00:34:00,083
[music continues]

554
00:34:00,666 --> 00:34:02,958
<i>If we possess that girl,</i>

555
00:34:03,041 --> 00:34:05,125
<i>even if Han knows she's a demon,</i>

556
00:34:05,208 --> 00:34:06,958
<i>he wouldn't dare hurt her.</i>

557
00:34:11,625 --> 00:34:13,625
- [ghost] Hmm.
- [dramatic music playing]

558
00:34:14,208 --> 00:34:17,333
Don't underestimate that brat.

559
00:34:17,833 --> 00:34:20,916
Remember he disposed of Chi-sha.

560
00:34:21,500 --> 00:34:23,416
You must tread carefully.

561
00:34:24,000 --> 00:34:26,083
This is the last step.

562
00:34:26,583 --> 00:34:29,375
Refine the corpse demons.

563
00:34:29,458 --> 00:34:33,833
Find a way to exhaust his magical tools.

564
00:34:47,875 --> 00:34:49,916
[music builds]

565
00:34:50,000 --> 00:34:51,416
[groans]

566
00:35:13,750 --> 00:35:15,083
[groans]

567
00:35:18,791 --> 00:35:20,583
[dramatic music continues]

568
00:35:20,666 --> 00:35:22,666
[growls]

569
00:35:26,916 --> 00:35:27,750
Huh.

570
00:35:33,125 --> 00:35:35,958
[roars loudly]

571
00:35:36,041 --> 00:35:38,041
[music stops abruptly]

572
00:35:41,041 --> 00:35:43,041
[theme music playing]

573
00:36:41,041 --> 00:36:43,041
[music continues]

574
00:37:41,041 --> 00:37:43,041
[music continues]

575
00:38:41,041 --> 00:38:43,041
[music continues]

576
00:39:35,666 --> 00:39:37,666
[music continues]

577
00:40:36,416 --> 00:40:38,416
[music ends]
